title: Optimize Wasm size and JavaScript interface
body:
With this PR, the size of the Wasm module has dropped from 1.23MB to 684KB, a 46% decrease.

* The `regex` crate no longer uses default features, reducing the size.
* The `url` crate was removed.
* For the Wasm target, YAML functionality is now left as an exercise for the consumer.  This removed the `serde_yaml` library and all its dependencies.
* Removed OpenAPI v2 schema.

This changes the JavaScript interface.  The `transpile` function now takes a JavaScript object and returns a JavaScript object.  This opens the door for more optimizations later, such as using serde-wasm-bindgen.

Closes #37.
